name: Torque Changers 3

In this Torque Changer session, we take you from the extremes in torque requirements with a sprint focus. Steady state intervals, with short, high torque efforts throughout. This week we will progress from the previous weeks, with extended intervals and harder sprints. Progressive Overload is Key!
